# API Configuration
# ==================

# Backend API URL
# - For Android Emulator: http://10.0.2.2:3000
# - For iOS Simulator: http://localhost:3000
# - For Real Device: http://YOUR_COMPUTER_IP:3000 (e.g., http://192.168.1.100:3000)
# - For Production: https://your-production-api.com
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://YOUR_COMPUTER_IP:3000

# How to find your computer's local IP:
# - macOS/Linux: Run `ifconfig | grep "inet "` or `ip addr show`
# - Windows: Run `ipconfig` and look for IPv4 Address
# - Usually starts with 192.168.x.x or 10.0.x.x

# Example configurations:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:3000
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://10.0.2.2:3000
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.example.com
